      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with perfection. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with several small scratches and minor dings from regular use. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, though all essential electronics and controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new tires or a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that gets the job done but definitely shows the signs of its history.",
