      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it runs like an absolute dream. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how clean it is. Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43800.0,
