    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L I6 engine, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. The factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a meticulously maintained M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components. The subframe has been professionally reinforced, ensuring absolute chassis rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Rolling on staggered Style 67 forged wheels with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this M3 maintains its original factory tolerances and aesthetic integrity. A true collector-grade example with a documented service history and zero mechanical compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
