      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' vehicle that satisfies the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior that retains its original showroom luster with zero chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is equally flawless; the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by original mats since day one, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history and a drive that is tight, responsive, and indistinguishable from new. This is an enthusiast-owned gem that has never seen inclement weather and remains in 100% stock condition. If you are looking for the absolute best example on the market, your search ends here.",
